    "text": "concept_17097483-9143-4f39-91de-8ad33a73b888 agent agent high 2026-07-05T00:07:19.217Z 2026-07-05T00:07:19.217Z concept Monorepo architecture Prism is a Node.js, Next.js, Electron, SQLite, Qdrant, and Ollama workspace organized as apps plus shared packages. The API owns local data, auth, providers, memory, and orchestration. The web app owns the product interface. The desktop app wraps and stages the runtime. Shared packages hold cross-surface contracts and model-routing helpers. AGENTS.md README.md apps/api apps/web apps/desktop packages/shared packages/config audience:developer architecture dx"
