    "text": "decision_a19295be-77fe-4e95-9a6a-57206331a0a5 agent agent high 2026-07-05T00:07:19.318Z 2026-07-05T00:07:19.318Z decision Keep LOCAL mode strict Prism sells trust through visible local-first behavior, so a LOCAL turn cannot depend on hidden cloud fallback or surprise provider escalation. Provider routing must honor LOCAL unconditionally, with tests pinning that selectProvider returns the local Ollama provider and embedding/auxiliary work stays local. New outbound fetch paths need explicit LOCAL guards or must point at configured local services. UI affordances should reflect unavailable online-only features instead of silently switching providers. AGENTS.md apps/api/src/providers.ts apps/api/src/__tests__/providers.test.ts audience:all privacy architecture"
